gether-for-the-matrix-themed-new-video-beautiful-scars-3833286">与大肖恩（Big Sean）</a> ，“你可以做到”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/will-smith-says-work-of-art-made-him-find-his-voice-dance-in-your-darkest-moments-album-3779400">“艺术品”（以他的儿子贾登（Jaden）和拉斯（Russ）为特色）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-will-smiths-assertive-new-single-tantrum-with-joyner-lucas-3822127">与乔伊纳·卢卡斯（Joyner Lucas）的“发脾气”以先前发行的单曲“美丽的伤痕”为特色</a>。</p><div class="wDYxhc" lang="en-GB" data-md="61"></div></div><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-hit-out-at-will-smith-for-inappropriate-on-stage-kiss-with-india-martinez-3841432">迷在威尔·史密斯（Will Smith）击中，因为与印度马丁内斯（Martinez）的舞台上“不合适”的吻</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
